OL,7,FA paedophile has been jailed for life
OL,8,Fafter admitting more than 10 sexual
OL,9,Foffences against children.
OL,11,FColin Morris, 48, from Ebbw Vale,
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to all offences,
OL,13,Fincluding three counts of rape of a
OL,14,Fchild under 13, two counts of attempt
OL,15,Frape, one count of inciting a child to
OL,16,Fengage in sexual activity, six counts
OL,17,Fof making indecent images of children
OL,18,Fand three counts of distributing
OL,19,Findecent images of children.
